| `solar_cycle_phase` | `sin(2π(year−2008)/11)` |
| `speed_excess` | `v_cme − v_sw` |
| `speed_ratio` | `v_cme / v_sw` |
| `ram_pressure` | `n_sw × v_sw²` |
